      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend section 230 of the Communications Act of 1934 to clarify that such section does not prevent a provider or user of an interactive computer service from being treated as the distributor of information provided by another information content provider, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
